data.description: Welcome to 1731 W Ashby Place, minutes away from WOODLAWN LAKE in the beautiful Thomas Jefferson High School Community! This great property is a 1-story home that is a gem on a dead-end street! Home features include 3 bedrooms, 1bath, 1 living area, 1 dining area, inside utility room and a leveled lot with a spacious backyard for entertaining or playground.  Come see this one before it is too late.
